Self-contained utility ported from GameNative with three capabilities:

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| [downloadSteam()](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/SteamClientManager.java#60-113) | Downloads `steam.tzst` with fallback URLs (GitHub → GameNative CDN) |
| [extractSteam()](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/SteamClientManager.java#154-187) | Extracts into Wine prefix at `C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\` |
| [runSteamless()](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/SteamClientManager.java#188-254) | Creates bat wrapper, runs `Steamless.CLI.exe`, swaps DRM-stripped exe |

